  <description type="morphology">Stems to 55 cm × 0.1--0.3 mm. Leaves 3.2--45.1 cm; blade 0.2--0.5 mm wide, apex acute. Inflorescences: peduncles with 5--30 coils, 30--300 × 0.5 mm. Flowers: pistils 4--6. Fruits 1.5--2 × 1.1--1.5 mm; gynophore 2--3.5 cm; beak lateral, erect, 0.5--1 mm. 2n = 40 (Europe).</description>
